title: The Story of 80s New Wave [Mix 1]
description:
I think I am notorious for uploading only non-mainstream 80's tunes, however I actually love many of the mainstream bands as well; the music I grew up with. I have made around 20 volumes of these mixes for my ipod and I thought you might want to get them as they are, mixed and ready to enjoy!
